The rule catalog, severity taxonomy (P0–P3), command vocabulary
(/audit, /critique, /polish, /typeset, /shape, etc.), and the "AI slop"
framing of design anti-patterns originate with that project. Detector
implementation in this repository is independent and targets `.pen`
files (the Pencil design tool format) rather than HTML/CSS/JSX.
